{"tid":1450673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷靜d，做好文宣先搞罷工同搞不合作運動","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:19.000Z","uid":60563,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"61f7c1c92a8d0fdf119e45c51449425424fead64","tid":1450673,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:48:52.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲，好似我咁依家都訓唔著<br />\n但越嬲越係要冷靜<br />\n請諗返上個月721單野，嗰日722立即搞不合作<br />\n點解會失敗?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為大家都未知發生乜事呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我同意行動要再升級<br />\n不過你地咁急會失撚晒焦點<br />\n機場可以繼續去做對外文宣<br />\n不過唔撚好搞不合作住，唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd540a9523e741bd7086e0a0a1f3fe1e106fce0","tid":1450673,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑社會死全家"},{"pid":"42aa8f2363bbfe4490d67e1b2e36ad9c3d8f56c9","tid":1450673,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77890f10c9fbe39549f0f22537d95b7d4ebc4058","tid":1450673,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11